data.description: This beautiful 6 bedroom/3.75 bath, 4,068 SQ FT home features an open concept main floor w/ an upper level & daylight basement! Hand scraped hardwoods flow throughout entry, kitchen, & dining nook. Kitchen is complete w/ quartz counter tops, full tile backsplash, double ovens & a HUGE fridge!  Master Suite is conveniently located on main floor w/ spa like 5 piece master bath & spacious walk in closet. Front & backyard landscaping w/ covered outdoor living area & gas fireplace! Move in Ready!
